===Uniques===
There is a 1/12 chance{{CiteNews|url=https://secure.runescape.com/m=news/fishing-trawler-improvements-and-equipment-rebalance-part-one?oldschool=1|title=Fishing Trawler Improvements and Equipment Rebalance: Part One|newsdate=21 April 2021}} that players will receive a piece of the [[angler's outfit]] they do not already own if the player had at least 50 contribution points. When equipped, pieces of the outfit grant a small [[experience]] bonus while [[Fishing]]. If the player's inventory is full and they attempt to pick up an outfit piece, the outfit piece will fall on the ground. The chance for a piece does not scale with the contribution meter beyond the initial reward unlock threshold of 50 points. Owning the [[spirit angler's outfit]] allows the player to receive a new angler's outfit drop from the trawler.

